; DISPLAY.DEF - module definition para Windows 1.x
; AUTO-GENERATED desde EGAHIRES.DRV (NE entry/relocation tables)

LIBRARY     DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION 'DISPLAY : 133, 96, 72 : EGA (more than 64K) with Enhanced Color Display'
EXETYPE     WINDOWS
STUB        'WINSTUB.EXE'

CODE        PRELOAD FIXED
DATA        PRELOAD FIXED SINGLE

